title: Sawbones: The Man Who Ate Everything
description:
This is a story about Tarrare. Tarrare was always hungry. Here is a list of some of the things Tarrare ate: A cat. A puppy. A snake. An eel. Offal. Poultices.

And maybe people.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
